   514→## 7. Accessibility Requirements
   515→
   516→### 7.1 Keyboard Navigation
   517→
   518→| Key | Action | Notes |
   519→|-----|--------|-------|
   520→| `+` / `=` | Zoom in | |
   521→| `-` / `_` | Zoom out | |
   522→| `0` | Reset zoom to 100% | |
