    72→    72→## 2. Mouse Events Reference
    73→    73→
    74→    74→### 2.1 Event Types
    75→    75→
    76→    76→| Event | Triggers | Properties |
    77→    77→|-------|----------|------------|
    78→    78→| `mousedown` | Button pressed | `button`, `buttons`, `clientX/Y` |
    79→    79→| `mouseup` | Button released | `button`, `buttons`, `clientX/Y` |
    80→    80→| `mousemove` | Cursor moved | `clientX/Y`, `movementX/Y` |
    81→    81→| `click` | Press + release (same element) | Fires after `mouseup` |
    82→    82→| `dblclick` | Two clicks within threshold | ~300ms default |
    83→    83→| `contextmenu` | Right-click | Prevent for custom menu |
    84→    84→| `wheel` | Scroll wheel rotated | `deltaX/Y/Z`, `deltaMode` |
    85→    85→| `mouseenter` | Cursor enters element | Does NOT bubble |
    86→    86→| `mouseleave` | Cursor leaves element | Does NOT bubble |
    87→    87→| `mouseover` | Cursor over element | Bubbles (includes children) |
    88→    88→| `mouseout` | Cursor leaves element | Bubbles (includes children) |
    89→    89→
    90→    90→### 2.2 Button Values
    91→    91→
    92→    92→| `event.button` | Description |
    93→    93→|----------------|-------------|
    94→    94→| 0 | Left button (primary) |
    95→    95→| 1 | Middle button (wheel click) |
    96→    96→| 2 | Right button (secondary) |
    97→    97→| 3 | Back button (browser) |
    98→    98→| 4 | Forward button (browser) |
