   564→   564→---
   565→   565→
   566→   566→## 8. Implementation Recommendations for MMS
   567→   567→
   568→   568→### 8.1 F118: Momentum Panning
   569→   569→
   570→   570→1. Track velocity during drag (store last 3-5 positions with timestamps)
   571→   571→2. On mouse up, calculate average velocity
   572→   572→3. Apply friction (0.93-0.95 per frame) in animation loop
   573→   573→4. Stop when velocity < 0.1 px/frame
   574→   574→5. Cancel momentum on any new interaction
   575→   575→
   576→   576→### 8.2 F119: Smooth Zoom
   577→   577→
   578→   578→1. Use `requestAnimationFrame` for zoom animations
   579→   579→2. Apply `Easing.quadOut` over 250ms
   580→   580→3. For pinch-zoom, apply zoom changes immediately (no animation)
   581→   581→4. Clamp zoom rate to prevent jumps
   582→   582→
   583→   583→### 8.3 F120: Double-Click Zoom
   584→   584→
   585→   585→1. Detect double-click with 300ms threshold
   586→   586→2. Convert click to world coordinates
   587→   587→3. Animate zoom 2x towards click point
   588→   588→4. Use 350ms duration with `cubicOut` easing
   589→   589→5. Respect MAX_ZOOM limit
   590→   590→
   591→   591→### 8.4 F121: Cross-Platform Scroll Normalization
   592→   592→
   593→   593→1. Use Facebook's normalization pattern (simplified)
   594→   594→2. Detect trackpad vs mouse by event frequency
   595→   595→3. Apply different sensitivity multipliers:
   596→   596→   - Mouse: `ZOOM_SENSITIVITY * 1.0`
   597→   597→   - Trackpad: `ZOOM_SENSITIVITY * 0.3`
   598→   598→4. Clamp zoom delta per event to ±0.5
   599→   599→5. Test on macOS, Windows, Linux (if available)
   600→   600→
   601→   601→---
   602→   602→
   603→   603→## 9. References
   604→   604→
   605→   605→### Official Documentation
   606→   606→- [MDN: Pinch zoom gestures](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Pointer_events/Pinch_zoom_gestures)
   607→   607→- [MDN: WheelEvent deltaMode](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/deltaMode)
