   613→   613→- [Figma: Adjust zoom and view options](https://help.figma.com/hc/en-us/articles/360041065034-Adjust-your-zoom-and-view-options)
   614→   614→- [Figma Forum: Scroll wheel zoom preference](https://forum.figma.com/ask-the-community-7/preference-for-scroll-wheel-on-your-mouse-to-zoom-in-and-out-feature-released-on-may-19th-35116)
