### LTTB Downsampling

For overview charts, use Largest-Triangle-Three-Buckets:

```typescript
import { processData } from 'downsample-lttb';

// Reduce 60,000 points to 500 for overview chart
const overviewData = useMemo(() => {
  if (data.length <= 500) return data;
  const xyData = data.map(d => [d.date.getTime(), d.value]);
  const downsampled = processData(xyData, 500);
  return downsampled.map(([time, value]) => ({
    date: new Date(time),
    value
  }));
}, [data]);
```

